T02TD2467E:141a-1: siddha sadm'a rga ni rna lam ta /
T02TD2467E:141a-3: grub pa dam pa'i lam nges pa /
T02TD2467E:141a-4: bcom ldan 'das 'jig rten dbang phyug la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2467E:141a-5: kha ras p'a ni 'jig rten dpal //
T02TD2467E:141a-6: thugs rje chen po ston pa'i mthus //
T02TD2467E:141b-0: gdul dka'i rang sems gdul ba @141b la ;
T02TD2467E:141b-1: / snying po bla med rnam gsum thob //
T02TD2467E:141b-2: kye ma ho 'dzam gling skye bo nyon //
T02TD2467E:141b-4: gang zhig 'ching bar byed pa'i rgyu //
T02TD2467E:141b-5: de nyid grol bar byed pa'i lam //
T02TD2467E:141b-6: sdug bsngal rgya mtsho sgrol ba'i gru //
T02TD2467E:141b-7: thub pa'i bstan pa rin po che //
T02TD2467E:141b-8: de yi ngo bo lam dang thabs //
T02TD2467E:141b-9: bshes gnyen kun dga'i gdams pa yin //
T02TD2467E:141b-11: mi lus rin chen rnyed par dka' //
T02TD2467E:141b-12: rnyed dka'i dal 'byor sprin ltar g-yo //
T02TD2467E:141b-13: 'khor ba thams cad sdug bsngal te //
T02TD2467E:141b-14: rang sems mya ngan 'das pa yin //
T02TD2467E:141b-15: rgya mtshor bying bas rnyed pa'i gru //
T02TD2467E:141b-16: chu rgyun drag po'i dpa' dang ni //
T02TD2467E:141b-17: dug can sbrul gyi tshang bzhin dang //
T02TD2467E:141b-18: ston gyi nam mkha'i gung bzhin no //
T02TD2467E:141b-19: longs spyod ci 'dra khyim gyi sbra //
T02TD2467E:141b-20: bshes pa ci 'dra tshong khang mi //
T02TD2467E:141b-21: rang lus ci 'dra sprul gyi lpags //
T02TD2467E:141b-22: tshe srog ci 'dra ri gzar chu //
T02TD2467E:141b-23: kye ma ho mi rtag srin po yi //
T02TD2467E:141b-24: khar chud ma gyur de srid bar //
T02TD2467E:141b-25: grogs dag srid pa ru bzlog la //
T02TD2467E:141b-26: sgrim par gyis shig bzhin bzang dag / sgyu ma'i grong khyer yangs pa na //
T02TD2467E:141b-27: rmi lam skyes bu longs spyod pa //
T02TD2467E:141b-29: snang sems de ltar shes par bya //
T02TD2467E:141b-30: ltos shig lus ni chu shing 'dra //
T02TD2467E:141b-31: dag ni brag ca mkha' 'dra yid //
T02TD2467E:141b-32: rdul tsam dmigs pa yod min na //
T02TD2467E:141b-33: bu dag gang la su zhig 'ching //
T02TD2467E:141b-34: yu bu thams cad da snyam dang //
T02TD2467E:141b-35: nga'o snyam dang gzhan snyam dang //
T02TD2467E:141b-36: gzhan gyi'o zhes log rtog pa //
T02TD2467E:141b-37: 'di dag ji ltar gang du dogs //
T02TD2467E:141b-38: ji ltar rmi lam bu shi ba //
T02TD2467E:141b-39: bu nyid med na de shi yang //
T02TD2467E:141b-40: bden par yod pa ma yin pa //
T02TD2467E:141b-41: de bzhin yu bu'i 'dzin pa yang //
T02TD2467E:141b-42: chos kun rmi lam 'dra ba'i phyir //
T02TD2467E:141b-43: zas gos nor dang grogs bshes dgra //
T02TD2467E:141b-44: sna tshogs snang ba 'di dag kun //
T02TD2467E:141b-45: sgyu ma yi ni rta glang bzhin //
T02TD2467E:141b-46: gang shar sor bzhag dran pa yin //
T02TD2467E:141b-47: dran pa rang grol bral ba ste //
T02TD2467E:141b-48: bral ba ro mnyam lhun gyis grub //
T02TD2467E:141b-49: snying po'i gseb lam rnam pa gsum /
